4Geeks Academy offers a comprehensive Cybersecurity Bootcamp designed for individuals with no prior experience aiming to become cybersecurity specialists. The program lasts 16 weeks, featuring three live online classes each week with a maximum of 16 students per class. Participants will learn key skills in Windows, Linux, network, and server administration, along with cloud security, penetration testing, and cyber threat intelligence analysis. Graduates receive an official completion certificate recognized by various institutions. The course content is available in both English and Spanish. For more information, visit [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/cybersecurity). stop